{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But when you get to Purdue and you're sitting there in this all white environment, now to be better than all those folk gets to be a very difficult one.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if you don't, if you aren't better, you feel like that that's failure.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you're gonna drop off the planet somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because you just won't make it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I remember when I went into a chemistry class.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When I was in Purdue, the first class I went into was a huge chemistry class, laboratory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this guy, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Miller, who was head of the chemistry department, told me-- and my mother said, never sit in the back of a room.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sit down front.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I got there, there was only seats were vacant when I finally found this crazy place were seats in the back.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I'm sitting in the back as the only black person in this sea of about 200 white kids.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and all males.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were engineers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he asked-- and he called my name and said, come down front.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went down wondering, what is this about?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went down, and he told me to open my hand, and he put a-- put the chemical blue vitriol in my hand and put water on it, and said, 'Go in the corner.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When it starts to sting you, you dance a little jig for us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I held my hand like this, and I went in the corner.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now you have to understand, now he's dealing with the discipline of an [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Indian. ?] I would stand there while it burned through my head before I'd even say anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm standing there and he finally said, that thing hasn't burned yet?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
